OL,6,FOn Tuesday, Edwards - who was the
OL,7,FBBC's highest-paid newsreader before
OL,8,Fhe resigned in April - admitted three
OL,9,Fcharges of making indecent images of
OL,10,Fchildren.
OL,12,FThe broadcaster was arrested in
OL,13,FNovember but his arrest was not made
OL,14,Fpublic until this week, when he was
OL,15,Fcharged.
OL,17,FCulture Secretary Lisa Nandy held
OL,18,Furgent talks with the broadcaster's
OL,19,Fdirector general Tim Davie on Thursday.
